Class ArchiveTransfer

  • Object
    • ArchiveTransfer

  • public class ArchiveTransfer
extends Object
    The Class ArchiveTransfer

    Class for the SEDA SIP manifest (document XML ArchiveTransfer in SEDA standard) content management. It contains all the elements declared in manifest, but also objects to manage the structure.

    It uses the generic DataObjectPackage class for DataObjet and ArchiveUnit structure.

      • toSedaXml

        public void toSedaXml(SEDAXMLStreamWriter xmlWriter,
                      boolean imbricateFlag,
                      SEDALibProgressLogger sedaLibProgressLogger)
               throws SEDALibException,
                      InterruptedException
        Export the whole structure in XML SEDA Manifest.
        Parameters:
        xmlWriter - the SEDAXMLStreamWriter generating the SEDA manifest
        imbricateFlag - indicates if the manifest ArchiveUnits are to be exported in imbricate mode (true) or in flat mode (false)
        sedaLibProgressLogger - the progress logger or null if no progress log expected
        Throws:
        SEDALibException - if the XML can't be written
        InterruptedException - if export process is interrupted
